Hip hop act Speed Darlington has stated that feeding is the only thing on the mind of most Nigerians. The ‘Bangdadadang’ singer said nothing else is weighty enough to bug the minds of Nigerians save the above-mentioned. “The only thing on the minds of Nigerians is daily bread, food; that’s it! Nothing else!!” he said. Reacting to his post, social media users expressed absolute agreement with his opinion though in differing ways. Amaradorisangel said: “Force the civilians into poverty and make them exchange their rights and dignity for food and handouts. The never-ending love story of Nigeria and its underdevelopment.” oluwakemi._o wrote: “He didn’t lie thou a hungry man is an angry man.” - Advertisement - Realjoehis stated: “That’s to tell you how worse it has become for the masses and that’s exactly where the politicians want the masses to be. But God will shame them 2023 #GetYourPVC.” beighdiva50 asked: “What else is more important?” oma__licha__ said: “Incoming president no lie at all.”   Whitemoney to hang out with Ojuelegba bridge co-tenants     TV actor Morgan Stevens found dead in kitchen     Ex-BBN’s Kiddwaya: My woman must have big heart   Mrlilgaga wrote: “Nigerians are just surviving, less than 5% of the population are actually living.” Ifeomaonye stated: “But what else should there be? No be who chop they see road think or plan? Speedy do giveaway or getat.” justdamz_ queried: “Well, if you no chop how you wan work?” moyamilia said: “Because that daily bread is important and not everyone can even afford it these days …..” q_meenahh wrote: “Na person wey eat go reason future o.” rashidatuumoru stated: “Wetin you want make I think? Food is life!” olat_boui quizzed: “Person wey never chop fit think straight?” bodybyteewhy said: “Daily bread is important.” dr_samsurge wrote: “Give us our daily bread ….so it’s important.” _squadrongram_ asked: “Wetin suppose dey our mind b4 Akpi?”